@startuml de1ux_statlord

actor User
participant "React Frontend" as Frontend
participant "Redux Store" as Store
participant "Django Backend" as Backend
database "PostgreSQL" as DB
participant "Display Device" as Device

User -> Frontend : Access dashboard editor
Frontend -> Store : Initialize state
Frontend -> Backend : Fetch initial data
Backend -> DB : Query data
DB --> Backend : Return data
Backend --> Frontend : Send data
Frontend -> Store : Update state

User -> Frontend : Create/Edit dashboard
Frontend -> Store : Update state
Frontend -> Backend : Save changes
Backend -> DB : Store changes
DB --> Backend : Confirm storage
Backend --> Frontend : Confirm save

User -> Frontend : Assign layout to display
Frontend -> Backend : Update display config
Backend -> DB : Store display config
DB --> Backend : Confirm storage
Backend --> Frontend : Confirm update

loop Every X seconds
    Frontend -> Backend : Poll for data updates
    Backend -> DB : Fetch updated data
    DB --> Backend : Return updated data
    Backend --> Frontend : Send updated data
    Frontend -> Store : Update state
    Frontend -> Frontend : Re-render dashboard
end

Frontend -> Device : Push display data
Device -> Device : Render dashboard

@enduml